data.description: Turnkey new construction w/ river views! This home features beautiful front covered deck, bright & airy living thru-out home w/ an abundance of natural light. Picturesque views from the living room w/ open floor plan thru kitchen. Oversized island in kitchen w/ butcher block counters, soft close cabinets & doors, tile back splash, recessed lighting & stainless appliances. Large utility/mudroom w/ storage & sink off back entrance. Spacious primary bed w/ attached bath, including walk in closet. 2 additional bedrooms & a full bath w/ shower/tub combo. Low maintenance landscaping. Exterior canned lighting around home, hot/cold exterior spigot & attached 2 car garage w/ car charger! Home is located close to public dock & walking trails.
